description:
This is a 44 minute workout called '45' RIDE - Who Runs The World' from the channel Kristina Girod.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor biking.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Nightclub Workout and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate and Beginner.
The effort required is Challenging.
